2580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1812580</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n2020普選主要行動：<br />\n1. 黎個遊行/集會向美領及國會提交普選細節，及寫信、twitter比國會議員，亦要叫IAD，攬炒團隊，gphone，現任立法會議員幫手（see post #1)<br />\n<br />\n2. 加入工會，全民三罷 逼港共中共退讓<br />\n（當年波蘭都係靠罷工lin贏共產政權<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B4Z-paCn0zr/?igshid=1jridkza9vxy8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB4Z-paCn0zr%2F%3Figshid%3D1jridkza9vxy8&d=bwUHcV0Pscj1NrVo4Cy%2FDQWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=a8122a68\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB4Z-paCn0zr%2F%3Figshid%3D1jridkza9vxy8&h=ed9878e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B4Z-paCn0zr/?igshid=1jridkza9vxy8</a> ）<br />\n<br />\n3. 尋求將普選放在trade deal phase 2<br />\n［國際戰線第一步］［聯署］將香港真雙普選推上中美貿易談判桌<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/appeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fappeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china&d=bwUHcV0Pscj1NrVo4Cy%2FDQWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=36d9b183\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/appeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china</a><br />\n<br />\n本地方面：謀求獨立，建立獨立意識<br />\n國際方面：揸住人權法核彈（取消優惠關稅地位）逼港共中共讓步下放政治權力"},{"pid":"cff1a3db3e33f174fd8b6cfd325f003bd1cece27","tid":1813801,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"025ac37877c19c8a279d4b357f278d0598b0a247","tid":1813801,"uid":25601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T13:59:40.000Z","msg":"佢話會定唔會"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T14:43:40.000Z","msg":"13秒  好有信心話唔會"},{"pid":"af841cf9832e8920f4517cccac63873d300164d8","tid":1813801,"uid":116054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"